                            <comment id="14408254" author="jdcasey" created="Fri, 15 Jul 2005 13:29:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Actually, the original discussion centered on adding this functionality to the ${plugin.&lt;b&gt;} arsenal, not the ${project.&lt;/b&gt;} one.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I think for consistency, I&apos;ll also add it to the MavenProject, but it definitely has to be on PluginDescriptor as well...&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14408291" author="jdcasey" created="Fri, 15 Jul 2005 14:05:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;use parameter expressions:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;  ${plugin.artifactMap}&lt;br/&gt;
  ${project.artifactMap}&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Artifacts in these maps are keyed using:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;  org.apache.maven.artifact.ArtifactUtils.versionlessKey( String groupId, String artifactId )&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;from the maven-artifact project.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
